## Child lane — refresh own slot when labels are stale

On a **spawned child** lane after the skill topic is clear:

1. Compare the visible tab title / hover to the work you are actually doing (skill path, plan slug, PR concern).
2. When spawn labels are **generic or wrong**, call MCP **`mission_control_update_lane_display`** on **this lane only** with non-empty **`title`** and, when useful, **`hoverDescription`** / **`description`** (respect max lengths in rule **9**).
3. **Skip** the MCP call when spawn labels already match the skill scope.
4. **Forbidden:** **`mission_control_update_dispatch_display`** from a child lane; editing **`dispatch-tab.v1.json`** or lane JSON by hand; asking the developer to rename tabs in the UI as a substitute.

---

## Squad Leader — dispatch chrome only

On the **Squad Leader** lane for **`plan and deliver`** (and other leader-led dispatches):

1. Update **`dispatchTitle`**, **`dispatchDescription`**, and **`dispatchHoverDescription`** via **`mission_control_update_dispatch_display`** when dispatch scope is clear — not child agent tab titles.
2. Update **leader slot row** copy via **`mission_control_update_lane_display`** only when patching the **leader's own** slot — not another agent's slot.
3. **Forbidden:** Using dispatch MCP to relabel child slots; prose-only "rename the coding-session tab to …" without the child lane calling lane MCP.

---

## Stale tab title recovery (orientation)

When the user asks why a tab still shows an old title after reload:

1. Re-read spawn context and rule **9** — durable labels come from **`dispatch-tab.v1.json`** (and governed MCP updates), not chat prose.
2. **Child lanes** refresh **own** slot via **`mission_control_update_lane_display`** when the child owns the correction.
3. **Squad Leader** refreshes **dispatch** chrome via **`mission_control_update_dispatch_display`** when the dispatch scope label is wrong.
4. If MCP fails or the wrong lane owns the update, use structured choice once — do not guess cross-slot permissions from **`git worktree list`** or transcript alone.

Full recovery steps: [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/docs/mission-control-display-metadata-host-spec.md`](docs/mission-control-display-metadata-host-spec.md) § *Stale tab title recovery*.

