## Relevant Links (documents)

**Documents ≠ display chrome.** Mid-session registration of authored/materially edited workspace paths uses MCP **`mission_control_update_relevant_documents`** on the **calling lane** — not **`mission_control_update_lane_display`** or **`mission_control_update_dispatch_display`**.

| Call | Skip |
|------|------|
| After Write/StrReplace that creates or materially edits ops plans, PRDs, brainstorm reports the lane wants in Relevant Links | Read-only loads; warm-up manifests; unchanged already-registered paths |

Normative Call/Skip, kind hints, and forbidden patterns: [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/README.md`](../missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/README.md) § *Relevant Links — post-write registration*. Platform display authority remains [rule **9**](.sedea/centers/sedea/rules/9_display-metadata-authority.mdc) — do not overload display MCP for documents.

